---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About Liz Liu | Liz Liu" description="Data scientist working across GenAI systems, experimentation, and business decisions." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="about-page">
			<header>
				<p class="about-label">ABOUT</p>
				<h1>I like problems that sit between a model and a decision.</h1>
			</header>

			<div class="about-grid">
				<aside>
					<div><span>Based in</span><strong>Singapore</strong></div>
					<div><span>Currently</span><strong>Iress</strong></div>
					<div><span>Previously</span><strong>Commonwealth Bank, ByteDance, ING</strong></div>
				</aside>

				<div class="about-copy">
					<p>I’m a data scientist focused on GenAI applications, rigorous experimentation, and the systems that turn uncertain model output into useful work.</p>
					<p>My work has ranged from production RAG and evaluation harnesses to real-time propensity models and advertising experiments. The common thread is translating technical complexity into a decision someone can trust.</p>
					<p>I’m interested in what happens after the demo: how a system is evaluated, where authority lives, what failure looks like, and whether the result changes a real business outcome.</p>
					<p>AI 对我来说不是信仰，也不是身份标签。它是一个帮助我整理混乱、扩大视野、推进想法的工具。</p>
					<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/liz-liu-a0b149167/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Connect on LinkedIn <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.about-page { width: min(100% - 3rem, 64rem); margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) 0 7rem; }
	.about-label { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #71717a; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 650; letter-spacing: 0.14em; }
	.about-page h1 { max-width: 15ch; margin: 0; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 610; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1; text-wrap: balance; }
	.about-grid { margin-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 14rem minmax(0, 38rem); gap: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 8rem); }
	.about-grid aside { border-top: 1px solid #d6d3d1; }
	.about-grid aside div { padding: 1rem 0; display: grid; gap: 0.15rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline); }
	.about-grid aside span { color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.09em; }
	.about-grid aside strong { color: #3f3f46; font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 550; }
	.about-copy p { margin: 0 0 1.5rem; color: #52525b; font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.8; }
	.about-copy p:first-child { color: #18181b; font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.4vw, 1.7rem); line-height: 1.6; }
	.about-copy a { margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-flex; color: #111; text-underline-offset: 4px; font-weight: 650; transition: transform 140ms var(--ease-out); }
	.about-copy a:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
	@media (max-width: 700px) {
		.about-page { width: min(100% - 2rem, 64rem); }
		.about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
	}
</style>
